the\n Universe. Then the smashana is only inside y=\r\nour heart, which in that case has become the whole world.&nbsp;Else, for th=\r\ne rest whose minds still firmly work in the field of duality, the smashana =\r\nis both outside and inside, depending on the degree of connection the perso=\r\nn has to the universal. Smashana Tara told Vimalananda that she cannot come=\r\n to his home, he has to go to the smashana every night. Thats the way it is=\r\n. Similarly, an ugra form is&nbsp;actually ferocious. A soumya form is actu=\r\nally non-ferocious.&nbsp;Some will love the former, some will love the late=\r\nr. Chandi, the very name, comes from the root word &quot;chand&quot;, which is also t=\r\nhe root word for Chandala. One who does not follow rules, cannot be made to=\r\n confirm to any rule, breaks down rules and restrictions.&nbsp;This derivat=\r\nion is mentioned in some of the texts on Chandi sadhana. That gives a sligh=\r\nt hint of what kind of energy She manifests.&lt;VAR id=3Dyui-ie-cursor&gt;&lt;/VAR&gt;&lt;=\r\n/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;-R=\r\negards&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&nbsp;Rajarshi&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;=\r\nRIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/D=\r\nIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif; FON=\r\nT-SIZE: 12pt&quot;&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times,=\r\n serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;FONT size=3D2 face=3DArial&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;BORDER-=\r\nBOTTOM: #ccc 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: #ccc 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; L=\r\nINE-HEIGHT: 0; MARGIN: 5px 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; HEIG=\r\nHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 0px; BORDER-TOP: #ccc 1px solid; BORDER-RIGHT: #ccc 1px=\r\n solid; PADDING-TOP: 0px&quot; class=3Dhr contentEditable=3Df